{"tid":901750,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"終於認左係為錢 雨革後去大陸做野","createTime":"2018-11-14T09:10:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-15T05:49:20.000Z","uid":38523,"like":7,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"d9d73e006c31bd7f59e27ff39621b5f6451cc318","tid":901750,"uid":38523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T09:10:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0sJWBPv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0sJWBPv.png&h=8d3871f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一個為錢可以雨革後去大陸做野既人<br />\n突然番香港搞所謂抗爭？<br />\n可以為錢輕易放棄底線<br />\n點知你會唔會為錢幫大陸做間碟？<br />\n依加你已經示範比廢老打都唔還手既另類左膠<br />\n同佢抗爭個班<br />\n自求多福啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔好講咁多廢話<br />\n當時可以為錢<br />\n雨革後都仆去大陸做野既人<br />\n咁輕易放棄底線<br />\n難保他日唔會又為錢出賣你？<br />\n為左錢完大陸會<br />\n突然番香港搞所謂抗爭？<br />\n就係比廢老打唔還手靠政府告？<br />\n咁耐以來你不停話人五毛原來你自己先係最大五毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span>"},{"pid":"af8044d80c9a718ce3d94f008f52a392a2b838ad","tid":901750,"uid":38523,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T09:12:34.000Z","msg":"關愛座hunter為錢去大陸就唔叫五毛<br />\n人地移民就叫五毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6589b8e4376cdfeacdca785b2f5acf0aa63fa6b5","tid":901750,"uid":164167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T09:13:05.000Z","msg":"系牙"},{"pid":"c775d999e711b0c3a6b8a5eda1dfc7add67b79f1","tid":901750,"uid":164167,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"af8044d80c9a718ce3d94f008f52a392a2b838ad","tid":9